stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Standby
    Standby --> Takeoff : CommandReceived
    Takeoff --> Cruise : TargetAltitudeReached

    Cruise --> ObstacleAvoidance : ObstacleDetected
    ObstacleAvoidance --> Cruise : WaypointClear

    Cruise --> WeatherEmergency : RainSensorTriggered
    Cruise --> LowBatteryFailsafe : BatteryUnder20Percent

    WeatherEmergency --> LocateNearestHub
    LowBatteryFailsafe --> LocateNearestHub

    LocateNearestHub --> DescentToHub : LandingSpotLocked
    LocateNearestHub --> LandImmediately : SearchTimeout

    DescentToHub --> SafeLanded
    LandImmediately --> SafeLanded
    SafeLanded --> [*]
